extends layout

block content
  section.xs-banner-sec.owl-carousel.banner-slider
    .banner-slider-item.banner-item1(style='background-image: url(/images/banner-slider/slider_1.jpg);')
      .slider-table
        .slider-table-cell
          .container
            .row.align-items-center
              .col-lg-10.offset-lg-1
                .banner-content.text-center
                  h2(style="font-size: 53px") A DIGITAL PLATFORM FOR AGRIBUSINESS
                  p
                    | Invest”N”farm is an innovative digital agritech crowdfunding platform focused on arable, pastoral farming and other agricultural operations in Africa
                  .xs-btn-wraper
                    a.xs-btn(href='/signup')
                      | Sign Up
    .banner-slider-item.banner-item1(style='background-image: url(/images/banner-slider/slider_2.jpg);')
      .slider-table
        .slider-table-cell
          .container
            .row.align-items-center
              .col-lg-10.offset-lg-1
                .banner-content.text-center
                  h2(style="font-size: 55px") INVEST IN FARMS...
                  h3.text-white
                    | Trade in Commodities           


  section.about-sec.section-padding
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-5.wow.fadeInUp.align-self-center(data-wow-delay='300ms' data-wow-duration='1.5s')
          .about-content
            h2.column-title
              span.xs-title Overview
              | Welcome to InvestNFarm!
            p Invest”N”Farm is an innovative digital agritech crowdfunding platform focused on arable and pastoral farming 
              | and other operations in Nigeria. We are registered in Nigeria as Invest”N”Farm Business Resources Limited 
              | (RC. 1791394). We believe strongly that agriculture is one of the most secured and profitable business to 
              | invest in as we provide opportunities to everyone to engage in Agribusiness anytime and on the go by investing 
              | in farms and trading commodities. We make it very simple for our investors in Nigeria and all over the world to 
              | invest with as little as possible and watch their investment grow. Our investors do not need to own a farm or be 
              | experienced in catering for the animals or crops. We take the burden off our investors and let them sit back and 
              | watch their money grow. Our investments are 100% safe and risk free.

        .col-md-7.align-self-center.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='400ms' data-wow-duration='1.5s')
          .about-video-item
            .about-video-img
              img(src='/images/corn.jpg' alt='')
            img.about-img2(src='/images/about_back.jpg' alt='')

  section.service-sec
    .service-sec-wrapper.section-padding(style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);")
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12
            .section-title-item
              h2.section-title
                | HOW IT WORKS
        .row.mt-4
          .col-lg-3.col-sm-6.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='300ms' data-wow-duration='1.5s')
            .single-service
              .service-img
                i.fa.fa-user-plus
              h3.xs-service-title
                a(href='#') SIGN UP
              p
                | Sign up for a complimentary Invest”N”Farm account to gain full access through profitable farmland investment opportunities in our user friendly portal.

          .col-lg-3.col-sm-6.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='400ms' data-wow-duration='1.5s')
            .single-service
              .service-img
                i.fa.fa-usd
              h3.xs-service-title
                a(href='#') INVEST
              p
                | Determine what best models fits your investment portfolio and invest. All opportunities have been carefully selected and offer high return possibilities.
          .col-lg-3.col-sm-6.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='500ms' data-wow-duration='1.5s')
            .single-service
              .service-img
                i.fa.fa-bullseye
              h3.xs-service-title
                a(href='#') TRACK
              p
                | Congratulations you’re an investor! Invest”N”Farm manages all aspects of the farmland, from planting to harvesting to selling while you simply track your farm’s progress online.

          .col-lg-3.col-sm-6.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='600ms' data-wow-duration='1.5s')
            .single-service
              .service-img
                i.fa.fa-handshake-o
              h3.xs-service-title
                a(href='#') RECEIVE
              p Profits from crop or animal sales are distributed to investors after they are harvested and sold. At the end of the holding period, investors will receive their share from the sale of the land.

                i.icon.icon-arrow-right

  section.recent-work-sec.section-padding
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-12
          .section-title-item
            h2.section-title
              |  OUR PROJECTS

      include includes/portfolios.pug

      .row
        .col-lg-12
          .load-more-btn
            a.xs-btn.fill(href='/projects') View More
  section.why-choose-us-sec.section-bg
    .why-choose-us-wrapper.section-padding(style="background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);")
      .container
        .row
          .col-lg-12.wow.fadeInUp.align-self-center(data-wow-delay='400ms' data-wow-duration='1.5s')
            .why-choose-content
              h2.column-title.text-center
                | WHY INVEST IN FARMLAND

              .row
                .col-sm-4
                  .single-why-choose-list
                    h4.text-green AN INDUSTRY THAT MATTERS
                    p Ownership in a farm operation allows investors to learn about the many aspects that go into a real working farm and the hard work that goes into feeding the world.
                .col-sm-4
                  .single-why-choose-list
                    h4.text-green DEMAND FOR FOOD
                    p By 2050 the world population will grow to over 10 billion people. An additional 3 billion people will enter the middle class causing food demand to sky rocket.
                .col-sm-4
                  .single-why-choose-list
                    h4.text-green MORE STABLE THAN STOCK MARKET
                    p Since farmland is uncorrelated with most other major asset classes, it has proven to perform well during challenging economic conditions.

                .col-sm-4
                  .single-why-choose-list
                    h4.text-green LONG TERM INVESTMENT STRATEGY
                    p Farmland is an attractive, long-term investment that has the potential to provide relative resiliency to challenging economic conditions.
                .col-sm-4
                  .single-why-choose-list
                    h4.text-green HISTORICAL RESILIENCE & POSITIVE RETURNS
                    p Historical data reveals that farmland has been an extremely resilient asset class. The industry has seen positive returns generated every year since 1990, proving it to be one of the most stable asset classes over the past few decades.
                .col-sm-4
                  .single-why-choose-list
                    h4.text-green HEDGE AGAINST INFLATION
                    p Over time, farmland has proven to have a positive correlation with inflation. More so than bonds, the stock market, and even gold. On average, no investment offers a hedge against inflation like farmland.


  section.latest-news-sec.section-padding
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-3.align-self-center.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='300ms' data-wow-duration='1.5s')
          .latest-news-content
            h2.column-title
              | More reasons why you should invest in farmland

        .col-lg-9
          .row
            .col-md-4.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='400ms' data-wow-duration='1.5s')
              .single-latest-news
                .single-news-content
                  h3.xs-post-title
                    a(href='#') Supply & Demand in Favor of Farmland Investing
                  p With a growing global population and shrinking, the laws of supply and demand are clearly in favor of farmland investing. As a result, farmland has consistently beat other asset classes over time.

            .col-md-4.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='500ms' data-wow-duration='1.5s')
              .single-latest-news
                .single-news-content
                  h3.xs-post-title
                    a(href='#') Social & Economic Benefits
                  p Investing in farmland benefits the investor more than just in financial gains. An investment in agriculture has social and economical benefits that include keeping farmers in the business of farming, keeping the world fed and clothed, bringing jobs and success to a community and supporting family businesses.

            .col-md-4.wow.fadeInUp(data-wow-delay='400ms' data-wow-duration='1.5s')
              .single-latest-news
                .single-news-content
                  h3.xs-post-title
                    a(href='#') Connection to the Industry that Feeds the World
                  p We believe that farmland is a different kind of asset. It's one that has so many interesting processes and produces a commodity that really matters; food. Visiting your piece of farmland and seeing it for yourself is a unique opportunity that we invite our investors to experience.									
  section.call-to-action-sec
    .container-fluid
      .row
        .col-lg-6.offset-lg-6.xs-padding-0.call-action-item
          .call-to-action-content
            h2.column-title.white
              span Start Investing
              br
              | Now
            p
              | Sign up to begin, or view our available projects
            .call-to-btn
              a.xs-btn.fill(href='/projects') Our Projects
              a.xs-btn(href='/signup') Sign Up
  .xs-map-sec
    .xs-maps-wraper
      .map
        iframe(src='https://maps.google.com/maps?width=100&height=600&hl=en&q=16,%20Adeniyi%20Jones,%20Victoria%20Island,%20Lagos.%20Nigeria.&t=&z=13&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed')
